TITLE
SCOTT BEATTIE OF ELIZABETH ARDEN



AUTHOR(S)
Naughton, Julie



PUB. DATE
December 2006



SOURCE
WWD: Women's Wear Daily;WWD BeautyBiz, Vol. 192 Issue 120, p31



SOURCE TYPE
Trade Publication 



DOC. TYPE
Article 



ABSTRACT
The article features Scott Beattie, chairman and CEO of Elizabeth Arden. Beattie has worked a deal with then-owner Unilever to purchase Elizabeth Arden and has rejuvenated the brand and the company. He has signed celebrities such as Britney Spears and Mariah Carey, launched a joint marketing agreement with Allergan for its Prevage brand and put in place a distribution strategy that includes moving Arden's prestige brands into the mass market.



